swaylock-plugin (1.8.6.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New binary package swaylock-plugin-screensaver: xscreensaver hack lock
    launcher with per-hack option support (hacks.conf), rofi picker with
    screenshot thumbnails and descriptions, and a local thumbnail generator
    (contrib/screensaver).
  * Source is now multi-binary: per-package install files, meson install
    staged in debian/tmp.

 -- syndr <syndr@ultroncore.net>  Mon, 06 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000

swaylock-plugin (1.8.6.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First fork release packaged for Debian/Ubuntu. Version distinguished
    from upstream 1.8.6 (v1.8.6 is an upstream tag).
  * Prebuilt .debs are distributed via GitHub Releases; the CI stamps a
    distro suffix (e.g. .ubuntu24.04.deb) on the file name only — the
    package version stays as recorded here.

